  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The first objection to P3 rests on the idea that intelligence and goals (values) are connected.",
    "According to this view, a being which is superior to humans in intelligence, e.g.",
    "an AGI, must have-or strongly tends to have-reasonable or ethical goals (Müller and Cannon 2022; Railton 2020).",
    "Proponents of this objection also adduce the observation that, in humans, learning of moral reasoning and learning of other cognitive abilities are interdependent.",
    "However, observations regarding human moral learning are irrelevant."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "an AGI, must have-or strongly tends to have-reasonable or ethical goals (Müller and Cannon 2022; Railton 2020)."
  ]
}